posts.subject: Other Boards and Pastebin
posts.body:
CYOA pastebin with useful links: https://pastebin.com/vrqYhnpu

The CYOA community might be too small for ZeroNet. Other than this board there is one on Millchan that is also inactive, a subreddit, and 4chan's /tg/ has generals. Anywhere else? 8chan's CYOA board was the only good one I knew of.
